      <h2>Building Sangha for Sustained Action</h2>
      <p>This call to action aspires to connect the already existing and diverse community of practitioners engaged and committed to nonviolent responses to suffering, as well as those wishing to find new ways to engage. Through collective practice of the 14 Mindfulness Trainings, we aspire to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create ongoing support for compassionate action</li>
        <li>Coordinate nonviolent responses to injustice</li>
        <li>Practice deep listening across difference</li>
        <li>Build bridges between communities</li>
      </ul>
      <p><em>We aspire to grow a network able to support existing and new local sangha organizing, study and practice spaces, and coordinated peaceful action.</em></p>
    </div>

